high_descs: Turn and walk towards the small black table next to the large white table.
Pick up the white mug with the spoon in it from the black table.
Turn around to walk towards the larger circular black table.
Set the white mug with the spoon down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Move a white mug with a spoon in it to the black circular table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small stand in the corner to your right.
Grab the mug with a spoon in it behind the sponge on the small stand.
Turn around and walk to the black round table straight ahead.
Place the mug with a spoon in it on the black round table.
anns.task_desc: Place the mug with a spoon in it on the black round table.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and turn to the right to face the small black table.
Pick the white mug up from the small black table.
Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the larger, round table.
Put the mug down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug on a table.
